author: Michael Connell
title: Michael Connell
text: Totally Wicked was the first place I ordered. Their customer service is outstanding. I've placed two orders here so far and will not go anywhere else. The shipping is Fast and their prices are great. They also have a great selection and get new things in all the time. I am a loyal customer for life. One big plus for me was they take paypal. Give them a try. You wont be sorry.
